data.description: Frisco City AL. A charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom + bonus room, home with unique character and a huge front and back yard on 2 acres of land. The 2018 Metal Roof, 2014 Electrical wiring and 2020 hot water heater are just a few replacements that have been made. Home is located close to shopping centers and schools. Home has screened in front porch entrance, covered back patio. Bedroom has walk in closet with a  jacuzzi in the nearest bathroom. Flooring consists of vinyl, tile and carpet. The backyard provides shade and fruit trees.  Home is move-in-ready!
